  <Operation Class="PatchOperationSequence" MayRequire="OskarPotocki.VanillaFactionsExpanded.SettlersModule">
    <success>Always</success>
    <operations>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemshine"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>rot gut</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemshine"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>A harsh, flammable wasteland liquor distilled from oil. Rot gut dulls pain and misery for a while, but it leaves the drinker soaked in volatile fumes and can turn a bad death into a fireball.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Plant_Chemroot"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>radseng</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Plant_Chemroot"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>A mutated offshoot of ginseng whose roots burrow deep through loose soil until they tap underground oil pockets. Farmers cultivate radseng for the oil-rich sludge in its roots, even though a bad spark can turn the field into an inferno.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="ChemBoiler"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>crude oil boiler</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemlamp"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>oil lamp</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="ChemlampPost"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>oil lamp post</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Building_ChemshineBarrel"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>rot gut barrel</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Building_ChemshineBarrel"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>A barrel for fermenting rot gut.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="TableFaro"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>caravan table</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="TableFaro"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>A travel-worn gaming table used for caravan games and roadside wagers. Allows up to two players at a time.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Building_ChemshineBarrel"]/notWorkingKey</xpath>
        <value>
          <notWorkingKey>This rot gut barrel is not working at the moment</notWorkingKey>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="SettlerCivil"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>These people have lived here for decades or centuries and lost most of the technology that first brought them to this world. They can still defend themselves with basic gunpowder weapons while going about their daily routine of herding cattle, drinking rot gut, and hunting down bounties.\n\nThey care about trade, trust, and survival.\n\nThis particular group holds civil behavior in high regard.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="SettlerRough"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>These people have lived here for decades or centuries and lost most of the technology that first brought them to this world. They can still defend themselves with basic gunpowder weapons while going about their daily routine of herding cattle, drinking rot gut, and hunting down bounties.\n\nThey are not concerned with trade or trust.\n\nThis particular group believes that no one is created equal, and only strength allows one to survive on the frontier.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemshined"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>rot gut</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemshined"]/labelNoun</xpath>
        <value>
          <labelNoun>rot-gutted</labelNoun>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Play_Faro"]/reportString</xpath>
        <value>
          <reportString>playing caravan cards.</reportString>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="VFES_ChemfuelToChemshine"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>Ferment oil into rot gut</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="VFES_ChemfuelToChemshine"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>Turns 50 oil into 25 rot gut.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="VFES_ChemfuelToChemshine"]/labelOverride</xpath>
        <value>
          <labelOverride>Ferment 50 oil into 25 rot gut</labelOverride>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="VFES_Bandits"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>Disabled Bandits</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="VFES_Bandits"]/description</xpath>
        <value>
          <description>This Settlers scenario has been disabled by Sunset.</description>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="Chemshined"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>rot-gutted</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="TakeChemshineOutOfChemshineBarrel"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>draw rot gut from rot gut barrels</label>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="TakeChemshineOutOfChemshineBarrel"]/verb</xpath>
        <value>
          <verb>draw rot gut</verb>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="TakeChemshineOutOfChemshineBarrel"]/gerund</xpath>
        <value>
          <gerund>drawing rot gut from</gerund>
        </value>
      </li>
      <li Class="PatchOperationReplace">
        <xpath>/Defs/*[defName="FillChemshineBarrel"]/label</xpath>
        <value>
          <label>fill rot gut barrels</label>
        </value>
      </li>
    </operations>
  </Operation>
</Patch>